## 25. Content Governance Framework

Every piece of content must be reviewed or filtered according to these criteria:

1. Age appropriateness
2. Educational/developmental value
3. Low stimulation level
4. No harmful language
5. No violence or fear-based content for young children
6. No sexual content
7. No manipulative ads
8. No infinite autoplay
9. No loot-box or gambling-like mechanics
10. Parent approval or trusted whitelist
11. Clear license or permission for use
12. Cultural sensitivity
13. Ability to support active engagement, not only passive viewing

